OL,3,CRoadwork-plagued M27 named as
OL,4,CEngland's worst motorway
OL,6,FThe M27 in Hampshire has been ranked
OL,7,FEngland's worst motorway, amid
OL,8,Fconcerns over roadworks and delays.
OL,10,FJust 56% of drivers who used the 28-
OL,11,Fmile road said they were satisfied
OL,12,Fwith their journey, a survey by
OL,13,Fwatchdog Transport Focus found.
OL,15,FOne respondent described roadworks on
OL,16,Fthe motorway as "terrible" as they
OL,17,Fcause reduced speed and narrow lanes
OL,18,Fdespite the respondent "very rarely"
OL,19,Fseeing any work happening.
OL,26,@xD@QOUxD@ZO]zD@XOUzD@dO]
