FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784630877
OL,3,CRoadwork-plagued M27 named as
OL,4,CEngland's worst motorway
OL,6,FThe road has seen long-running work
OL,7,Ffor surfacing and junction
OL,8,Fmodifications.
OL,10,FKent's M20 was ranked the country's
OL,11,Ffavourite motorway, with a
OL,12,Fsatisfaction rating of 79%.
OL,14,FAcross all motorways and major A
OL,15,Froads, 71% of drivers were satisfied
OL,16,Fwith their journey, up from 69% last
OL,17,Fyear.
OL,19,FRatings for journey times, road
OL,20,Fsurfaces and roadworks management all
OL,21,Fimproved year-on-year.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
