OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784630877
OL,3,CRoadwork-plagued M27 named as
OL,4,CEngland's worst motorway
OL,6,FEngland's network of motorways and
OL,7,Fmajor A roads is entering one of its
OL,8,Flargest maintenance periods since much
OL,9,Fof it was first built in the 1960s.
OL,11,FNational Highways is embarking on a
OL,12,Ffive-year renewals programme as part
OL,13,Fof the third Road Investment Strategy,
OL,14,Fwhich is likely to involve more
OL,15,Froadworks.
OL,17,FTransport Focus director Louise
OL,18,FCollins said the survey results
OL,19,Fdemonstrate that "positive
OL,20,Fimprovements to the road user
OL,21,Fexperience are possible".
OL,26,@{D@ROU}D@XO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784630877
OL,3,CRoadwork-plagued M27 named as
OL,4,CEngland's worst motorway
OL,6,F"Overall satisfaction has increased
OL,7,Fand there are encouraging signs that
OL,8,Fdrivers are noticing improvements in
OL,9,Fkey areas, however drivers continue to
OL,10,Ftell us that roadworks can make or
OL,11,Fbreak a journey," she added.
OL,13,F"By applying the positive lessons from
OL,14,Frecent schemes, National Highways has
OL,15,Fan opportunity to ensure roadworks are
OL,16,Fwell planned, clearly communicated and
OL,17,Fminimise disruption wherever possible."
OL,19,FSatisfaction with journeys on smart
OL,20,Fmotorways rose from 60% last year to
OL,21,F66%.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@QO]uD@AOUyD@gO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
