OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784630877
OL,3,CRoadwork-plagued M27 named as
OL,4,CEngland's worst motorway
OL,6,FTransport Focus attributed this to the
OL,7,Fcompletion of work to retrofit 150
OL,8,Fadditional emergency refuge areas,
OL,9,Fwhich involved widespread roadworks
OL,10,Fcausing delays.
OL,12,FDrivers on sections of smart motorway
OL,13,Fcontinued to feel less safe than those
OL,14,Fon conventional motorways, at 78% and
OL,15,F82% respectively.
OL,17,FThe A30, which runs between west
OL,18,FLondon and Cornwall, was ranked the
OL,19,Fbest A road, with a 79% satisfaction
OL,20,Fscore.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784630877
OL,3,CRoadwork-plagued M27 named as
OL,4,CEngland's worst motorway
OL,6,FAt the other end of the scale, the A12
OL,7,Fbetween the east of the capital and
OL,8,FSuffolk had the lowest rating, at 64%.
OL,10,FSteve Gooding, director of motoring
OL,11,Fresearch charity the RAC Foundation,
OL,12,Fsaid there is an "important link
OL,13,Fbetween road users' satisfaction and
OL,14,Fhow well they feel roadworks are being
OL,15,Fmanaged".
OL,26,@tD@ROUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
