OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784630877
OL,3,CRoadwork-plagued M27 named as
OL,4,CEngland's worst motorway
OL,6,FHe said: "The picture that emerges
OL,7,Fsuggests National Highways will need
OL,8,Fto up its game more consistently
OL,9,Facross England given the scale of
OL,10,Fmaintenance work planned for the
OL,11,Fnetwork through to 2030."
OL,13,FA National Highways spokesperson said:
OL,14,F"We manage our roads to ensure the
OL,15,Fhighest levels of safety while
OL,16,Fminimising disruption to drivers.
OL,18,F"The survey results show our work to
OL,19,Fimprove road conditions and incident
OL,20,Fresponse times have had a positive
OL,21,Fimpact for drivers.
OL,26,@nD@JOUsD@YO]vD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
