OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784630877
OL,3,CRoadwork-plagued M27 named as
OL,4,CEngland's worst motorway
OL,6,F"When roads are well maintained,
OL,7,Fbusinesses and communities feel the
OL,8,Fbenefit, and we are committed to
OL,9,Ftackling an ageing network head-on to
OL,10,Fkeep the country moving and give
OL,11,Fdrivers better experiences."
OL,13,FThe survey of more than 9,500 drivers
OL,14,Fwas conducted in the 12 months to the
OL,15,Fend of March.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@\O]
